===============================================================================
1. ContactClientFragX - Overview
===============================================================================
ContactClientFragX takes the ContactClientFrag application at:
	https://github.com/ronlemire2/ContactClientFrag
and makes it compatible with pre-3.0 versions of Android.

To do this ContactClientFragX uses:
	1) ...\android-sdk\extras\android\support\v4\android-support-v4.jar
	2) ...\android-sdk\samples\android-14\ActionBarCompat
from the Android setup folder.

